These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, reading, dancing, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, crime, zombie, western
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, august, june, july
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1
5. the person watching crime movies is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's hobby is reading##2
6. the person who's birthday is in august is the person watching zombie movies##1
7. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Hobby        | dancing | writing  | reading | puzzles  |
| Movie-Genre         | western    | crime  | fantasy       | zombie     |
| Birthday   | june     | march | july       | august |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, february, january, june
4 different games are played: go, domino, monopoly, may
City: boston, san-francisco, berlin, liverpool
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is between the person playing may and the person who's birthday is in june##2
5. the person playing may is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
6. the person playing go is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
7. the person playing monopoly is the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Birthday         | february | may    | june  | january |
| Game   | may  | go  | domino   | monopoly    |
| City         | san-francisco | liverpool | boston | berlin      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, water-polo, basketball, snowboarding
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, trike, helicopter, roller
4 different games are played: monopoly, canasta, poker, whist
1. the person playing canasta is between the person playing whist and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
2. the person driving the train is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1
6. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
7. the person playing poker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Sport      | water-polo | snowboarding         | ice-hockey   | basketball    |
| Transport         | trike | roller | train | helicopter |
| Game   | poker   | canasta        | whist      | monopoly   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, swisher, alhambra, pall-mall
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, orange, turquise, aquamarine
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, january, april, november
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in november and the pall-mall-smoker##2
3. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
5. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who likes blue and the person who's birthday is in january##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Cigar   | pall-mall        | swisher   | old-henry | alhambra |
| Color         | turquise | blue | orange    | aquamarine |
| Birthday     | april       | march     | november       | january    |

