.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, colombian, nigerian, chinese
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, romance, thriller, adventure
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, metal, soul, house
1. the fan house is between the american and the colombian##2
2. the fan house is the chinese##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
4. the colombian is on the left of the nigerian##1
5. the fan disco is on the right of the fan soul##1
6. the fan soul is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
7. the fan house is between the fan soul and the person watching martial-arts movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Nationality   | american | chinese      | colombian       | nigerian   |
| Movie-Genre      | martial-arts   | romance  | adventure | thriller     |
| Music-Genre      | metal     | house | soul        | disco |

