.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, november, may, october
4 different games are played: bridge, scrabble, canasta, poker
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite, hot-chocolate, coffee
1. the person playing poker is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the person playing bridge is between the person playing poker and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
6. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in may##2
7. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Birthday    | may | november  | august | october      |
| Game   | canasta  | poker  | bridge | scrabble |
| Beverage   | coffee | fanta | sprite | hot-chocolate     |

