.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, tram, scooter, skateboard
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, april, october, december
4 different games are played: backgammon, monopoly, mah-jongg, domino
1. the person playing domino is the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
6. the person driving the tram is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in october##2
7. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Transport          | scooter  | tram    | skateboard | airplane  |
| Birthday   | october | december       | april        | august    |
| Game         | monopoly | backgammon | domino  | mah-jongg |

