.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, engineer, scientist, police-officer
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, light-blue, blood-red, mauve
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, turkish, colombian, pakistani
1. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the australian##1
2. the person who likes light-blue is between the pakistani and the engineer##2
3. the scientist is on the right of the colombian##1
4. the colombian is on the right of the australian##1
5. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the police-officer##1
6. the scientist is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Job         | police-officer  | engineer | scientist | entrepreneur |
| Color   | azure  | mauve | light-blue   | blood-red         |
| Nationality           | australian | colombian  | turkish   | pakistani      |

