.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
City: miami, marseilles, berlin, boston
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, tulip, bellflower, iris
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, december, october, april
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person who growstulip is the person traveling to miami##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
4. the person who growsbellflower is the person traveling to marseilles##1
5. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
6. the person who growsbellflower is on the far right##1
7. the person who growstulip is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who growssunflower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| City          | boston  | miami    | berlin | marseilles       |
| Flower         | iris | tulip | sunflower  | bellflower |
| Birthday   | october   | april      | december  | september     |

