3. the fan r&b is between the fan pop and the person drinking 7up##2
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the fan jazz##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the bus is on the right of the fan jazz##1
7. the person driving the train is the person drinking cola##1
8. the person driving the snowmobile is the fan jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Music-Genre          | trance      | jazz | r&b | pop |
| Beverage         | cola   | 7up  | milk | iced-tea |
| Transport   | train | snowmobile   | bus | airplane |

