There are 4 different favourite colors: red, green, emerald, blood-red
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, july, august, february
1. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is the person traveling to miami##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who likes green and the person who likes emerald##2
4. the person who likes emerald is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person traveling to paris##2
5. the person who likes emerald is the person who's birthday is in february##1
6. the person who likes red is the person who's birthday is in july##1
7. the person who likes blood-red is the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| City    | paris  | edinburgh | hamburg | miami     |
| Color   | red | emerald   | blood-red  | green    |
| Birthday     | july        | february       | october      | august |

