.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-12::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, light-blue, white, orange
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, dancer, police-officer, scientist
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, horror, zombie, superhero
1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
2. the scientist is the person who likes white##1
3. the person who likes light-blue is between the person who likes white and the dancer##2
4. the police-officer is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
6. the person watching adventure movies is on the far right##1
7. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who likes white##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Color   | orange | white     | light-blue | fuchsia       |
| Job      | police-officer  | scientist | doctor  | dancer |
| Movie-Genre        | superhero  | horror      | zombie        | adventure      |

