1. the cottage house is the montecristo-smoker##1
2. the old-henry-smoker is the person drinking fanta##1
3. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
4. the colonial house is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
5. the havana-smoker is between the wooden house and the person drinking fanta##2
6. the montecristo-smoker is on the far right##1
7. the havana-smoker is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage           | tea | juice | fanta    | mirinda   |
| House   | wooden      | victorian   | colonial | cottage |
| Cigar     | aristoff     | havana       | old-henry        | montecristo    |

