4. the person who likes ebony is on the far left##1
5. the craftsman house is between the fan dubstep and the person who likes amber##2
6. the fan indie is on the left of the cottage house##1
7. the cottage house is between the farmhouse house and the craftsman house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
