.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, chinchilla, mouse
4 different games are played: chess, go, monopoly, snooker
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, game, vegafina, havana
1. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
2. the person playing monopoly is between the owner of the mouse and the vegafina-smoker##2
3. the havana-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
4. the swisher-smoker is on the far right##1
5. the person playing chess is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
6. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
7. the owner of the chinchilla is the swisher-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Pet   | bird    | frog | mouse           | chinchilla |
| Game       | chess | monopoly    | go          | snooker   |
| Cigar      | vegafina  | game   | havana | swisher  |

