.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-18::.
4 different games are played: bridge, chess, go, backgammon
The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, mechanic, librarian, architect
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, aquamarine, lilac, yellow
1. the librarian is the person playing chess##1
2. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
3. the architect is on the right of the person playing go##1
4. the person playing bridge is between the librarian and the chef##2
5. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
6. the person who likes yellow is between the person playing chess and the person who likes grey##2
7. the architect is the person who likes yellow##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Game      | go | bridge | chess     | backgammon   |
| Job   | chef | architect        | librarian  | mechanic  |
| Color           | grey      | yellow         | aquamarine | lilac |

