.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
4 different games are played: domino, snooker, billiard, bridge
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, rugby, badminton, poping
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, country, blues, pop
1. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left##1
2. the person playing domino is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the fan country is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
5. the fan pop is the person who's sport is poping##1
6. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person playing bridge and the fan blues##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Game        | bridge | snooker | domino | billiard |
| Sport         | baseball       | rugby     | badminton   | poping   |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | country | blues | pop |

 